These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, dancing, hiking, reading, singing
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, pakistani, russian
5 different games are played: backgammon, domino, whist, chess, snooker
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, lacrosse, skiing, swimming
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the brazilian##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the chinese##1
 5. the person playing domino is the pakistani##1
 6. the british is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the british is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the british##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
11. the person playing domino is the person who's sport is baseball##1
12. the person playing whist is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Hobby         | dancing  | baking    | reading | hiking    | singing  |
| Nationality   | british  | brazilian | chinese | pakistani | russian  |
| Game           | backgammon     | snooker     | chess  | domino   | whist    |
| Sport         | lacrosse | skiing    | cycling | baseball  | swimming |

