10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the dutch##1
11. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
12. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
13. the person watching mystery movies is the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
