 9. the person driving the boat is on the left of the engineer##1
10. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
11. the designer is the person eating cherry##1
12. the person driving the tram is the person who likes emerald##1
13. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
