The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, snowmobile, train, tram
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of punk is the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 4. the fan of blues is the thai##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 7. the fan of pop is the british##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
11. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
12. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
13. the argentine is the person who's birthday is in may##1
14. the polish is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
